    <item>
      <title>英伟达市值超越亚马逊</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/nvidia-overtakes-amazon-in-market-value-amid-scorching-rally</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英伟达公司(Nvidia Corp.)的市值周一超过了亚马逊公司(Amazon.com Inc.)，这是过去一年因人工智能计算芯片需求飙升而实现惊人反弹的最新里程碑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/nvidia-overtakes-amazon-in-market-value-amid-scorching-rally</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 16:29:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特鲁多政府因流行病旅行应用程序遭到审计员的猛烈抨击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trudeau-government-slammed-by-auditor-over-pandemic-travel-app</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大审计长针对一款在 Covid-19 大流行期间仓促开发的边境海关应用程序发布了一份措辞严厉的报告，称政府的“文件、财务记录和控制非常糟糕”，以至于无法准确确定成本。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/trudeau-government-slammed-by-auditor-over-pandemic-travel-app</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 16:11:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>惠普因自主欺诈向林奇索赔 40 亿美元损失</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/hp-seeks-4-billion-in-losses-from-mike-lynch-and-cfo-over-autonomy-fraud</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伦敦法官发现 Autonomy Corp. 的前老板在出售前以欺诈手段抬高公司价值后，惠普企业公司 (Hewlett Packard Enterprise Co.) 正在向 Autonomy Corp. 的前老板索要高达 40 亿美元的赔偿。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/hp-seeks-4-billion-in-losses-from-mike-lynch-and-cfo-over-autonomy-fraud</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 13:24:30 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>ContextLogic 以接近 1.73 亿美元的价格将 Wish 出售给 Qoo10</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/contextlogic-said-to-near-173-million-sale-of-wish-to-qoo10</link>
      <description><![CDATA[折扣在线零售商 Wish 的母公司已同意以 1.73 亿美元的价格将其资产和负债出售给新加坡电子商务公司 Qoo10。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/contextlogic-said-to-near-173-million-sale-of-wish-to-qoo10</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 12:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>荷兰法院下令停止向以色列运送 F-35 零部件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/dutch-ordered-to-halt-shipments-of-f-35-parts-to-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[荷兰一家法院命令荷兰停止向以色列运送 F-35 战斗机零部件，理由是加沙地带持续的军事袭击存在违反人权法的“明显风险”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/dutch-ordered-to-halt-shipments-of-f-35-parts-to-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 10:58:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>摩根士丹利表示，企业前所未有地关注成本</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/us-companies-are-discussing-cost-cuts-and-ai-like-never-before</link>
      <description><![CDATA[摩根士丹利策略师的分析显示，在推动资金重新分配和新技术投资的推动下，美国公司正在以创纪录的速度在财报电话会议上讨论成本控制问题。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/us-companies-are-discussing-cost-cuts-and-ai-like-never-before</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 10:34:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>部长表示，沙特阿美产能暂停是由于能源转移</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/aramco-s-capacity-halt-due-to-energy-transition-minister-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[能源部长阿卜杜勒阿齐兹·本·萨勒曼亲王表示，沙特阿美公司决定停止扩大产能是因为能源转型。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/aramco-s-capacity-halt-due-to-energy-transition-minister-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 08:25:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Believe 首席执行官提出以 14.6 亿欧元收购唱片公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/believe-founder-offers-to-buy-music-label-in-1-46-billion-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Believe SA 创始人 Denis Ladegaillerie 与投资公司合作，提出将公司私有化的要约，该法国唱片公司的估值为 14.6 亿欧元（15.8 亿美元），在 2021 年首次公开募股后，其股价下跌了 36% 。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-02-12/believe-founder-offers-to-buy-music-label-in-1-46-billion-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Feb 2024 08:05:52 GMT</pubDate>
